name: Little Boys Birthday Invitations 2
description:
$2.10 per invite minimum of 10

These invitations are single sided and printed on high quality photographic paper (6x4 inches). Each invitation has a magnet on the back.

If you require different sizing, colours, paper or double sided printing please contact us.

If you can’t find what you are looking for, we will work with you to create your custom design.

If you wish to print the invites yourself and you are only after a soft copy, please drop us a line.

For orders over $100 free shipping.

 Procedure:
1. Place your order here. Payment is done via Paypal. Please contact us, if you wish to pay via direct debit. 

2. After placing your order, send an email to: invitingprints@gmail.com, include your text information and any other customisation requests.

3. A digital proof will be e-mailed to you for your approval.

4. After we receive your approval your order will arrive within 3-5 business days (Australia wide).  Please allow 7-15 working days for International delivery.
